Name: DiagnosisVS
Title: ValueSet of the Diagnostic Evidence Base
Descriptino: This ValueSet indicates which diagnostic evidence base was used for its realization

Name: DischDestVS
Title: ValueSet of Discharge Location
Descriptino: Discharge destination following acute care hospitalization. What type of place was the patient discharged to?

Name: EstStrokeSevNIHSSCatVS
Title: ValueSet that categorizes the estimated severity of the stroke using the NIHSS according to the ICHOM standard.
Descriptino: This ValueSet is intended to categorize the severity of the stroke based on the National Institutes of Health Stroke Scale (NIHSS).

Name: GenderIdentityVS
Title: ValueSet of Gender Identity
Descriptino: ValueSet for Gender Identity based on LOINC.

Name: LiveAlonePreVS
Title: ValueSet of Live Alone Pre-Stroke
Descriptino: ValueSet indicating whether a patient lived alone prior to a stroke event based on ICHOM terminology.

Name: LivingLocPreVS
Title: ValueSet of Patient's Residence Prior to a Stroke
Descriptino: Represents the patient's most recent place of residence before the occurrence of a stroke based on ICHOM code.

Name: NoYesUnknownVS
Title: ValueSet Yes
Descriptino: No and Unknown
Uses: ValueSet with responses Yes, No, and Unknown

Name: PROMIS10VS
Title: ValueSet of PROMIS-10 Response Questionnaire
Descriptino: This ValueSet defines the response values for the PROMIS-10 (Patient-Reported Outcomes Measurement Information System 10-item short form) Questionnaire.

Name: SMRSqVS
Title: ValueSet of simplified modified Ranking Scale questionnaire (SMRSq)
Descriptino: This ValueSet defines the response values for the simplified modified Ranking Scale questionnaire.

Name: SmokingStatusVS
Title: ValueSet of Smoking Status
Descriptino: ValueSet for Smoking Status. A person's current and past smoking behavior.

Name: StrokeAmbVS
Title: ValueSet of Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Ambulation
Descriptino: This ValueSet defines the response values for the Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Ambulation.

Name: StrokeDressingVS
Title: ValueSet of Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Dressing
Descriptino: This ValueSet defines the response values for the Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Dressing.

Name: StrokeSevLocVS
Title: ValueSet Categorizing the State of Consciousness according to the ICHOM standard.
Descriptino: This ValueSet is based on the ICHOM standard and it indicates the patient's state of consciousness as measured upon arrival at the reference hospital.

Name: StrokeToiletingVS
Title: ValueSet of Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Toileting
Descriptino: This ValueSet defines the response values for the Prestroke and Poststroke Functional Status: Toileting.

Name: StrokeTypeVS
Title: ValueSet for stroke type based on ICHOM
Descriptino: This ValueSet aims to categorize the stroke type according to the ICHOM standard.

Name: SymtDurVS
Title: ValueSet Categorizing the Duration of Stroke Symptoms
Descriptino: ValueSet that categorizes the duration of stroke symptoms, considering the time from symptom onset to admission at the reference hospital.

Name: CNES_ValueSet
Title: ValueSet of National Registry of Health Establishments (CNES - Cadastro Nacional de Estabelecimentos de Saúde)
Descriptino: This ValueSet details codes for Stroke Healthcare Units in Joinville based on National Registry of Health Establishments (CNES - Cadastro Nacional de Estabelecimentos de Saúde).

Name: HospitalDepartment_ValueSet
Title: ValueSet for Hospital Department
Descriptino: This ValueSet includes the hospital departments responsible for taking care of stroke patients.

Name: CardiovascularComorbidities_ValueSet
Title: ValueSet of Cardiovascular Comorbidities
Descriptino: Indicate which comorbidities the patient is living with. Select all conditions that apply at every annual follow-up.

Name: MolicAVC_ReferenceLocation_ValueSet
Title: ValueSet of Reference Location
Descriptino: Indicate and classify where the patient was referred.

Name: ProfessionalCode_ValueSet
Title: ValueSet of Professional Code
Descriptino: This ValueSet is integral to the Molic-AVC project and details codes for professionals serving stroke patients in Brazil.

Name: MolicAVC_CodeHealthcareUnitValueSet
Title: Type of Healthcare Unit ValueSet
Descriptino: This ValueSet details codes for healthcare units serving stroke patients in Brazil.
